"snippet" : "AND The IEC operator is used for the bitwise AND of bit operands. When the input bits all yield 1, the output bit also yields 1; otherwise 0. Permitted data types: BOOL , BYTE , WORD , DWORD , LWORD Examples Result in var1: 2#1000_0010 ST var1 := 2#1001_0011 AND 2#1000_1010; FBD...", 
