"snippet" : "Partial access is possible only if the called expression has a conforming type and the partial index is less than or equal to the maximum partial index. Otherwise a compiler error is reported. Partial Type Access Type Maximum of Partial Index X BYTE 7 WORD 15 DWORD 31 LWORD 63 B BYTE 0 WORD 1 DWORD ...", 
