"snippet" : "C0006 Message : '<operator>' expected instead of '<token>' Possible error cause : Syntax error Error correction : Use the correct syntax. Example of the error: PROGRAM PLC_PRG VAR x: INT; bTest : BOOL; END_VAR IF bTest x := 9; END_IF Message: C0006: 'THEN' expected instead of 'x'...", 
