"snippet" : "C0008 Message : Unexpected end-of-file found: '<operator>', '<operator>', or '<operator>' expected Possible error cause : Syntax error Error correction : Use the correct syntax. Example of the error: PROGRAM PLC_PRG VAR x: INT; bTest : BOOL; END_VAR IF bTest THEN x := 9; Message: C0008: Unexpected e...", 
