"snippet" : "C0018 Message : <expression> is not a valid assignment target Possible error cause : An expression with no write permission is on the left side of an assignment. Example: a constant. Error correction : Assign only to variables that have write access. Example of the error: PROGRAM PLC_PRG VAR i: INT;...", 
