"snippet" : "C0020 Message : '<statement>' is no valid statement Possible error cause : Syntax error (for example, too few or too many characters) Error correction : Make sure that the syntax is correct. Example of the error: PROGRAM PLC_PRG VAR x : INT; END_VAR x = 2; Message: C0020: '(x = 2); ' is no valid sta...", 
