"snippet" : "C0031 Message : Type definition expected instead of '<no data type>' Possible error cause : An invalid type definition is assigned to the identifier. Error correction : Specify a valid type definition. Example of the error: PROGRAM PLC_PRG VAR i : 0; END_VAR Message: C0031: Type definition expected ...", 
