"snippet" : "C0051 Message : Single byte string expected for an attribute value instead of '<value>‘. Possible error cause : A string does not appear at the displayed location as expected. Error correction : Replace the current value with a string. Example of the error: PROGRAM PLC_PRG {IF hasattribute(pou: MyPO...", 
