"snippet" : "C0061 Message : Bitaccess on function call is not allowed Possible error cause : Bit access is performed on a function. Error correction : Use bit access only for supported data types. Example of the error: PROGRAM PLC_PRG VAR END_VAR Test().2; FUNCTION Test : INT VAR_INPUT END_VAR Message: C0061: B...", 
