"breadcrumbs" : "CODESYS Essentials \/ Reference: User Interface \/ Dialogs \/ Dialog: Options \/ Dialog: Options: Sequence Editor ", 
"snippet" : "Sequence editor Symbol: Function : The dialog contains the settings for the sequence editor . Call : Tools → Options command, Sequence editor category General Selection of elements which CODESYS displays in the sequence step of the sequence editor Appearance Defines the appearance of the sequence st...", 
