"breadcrumbs" : "CODESYS Essentials \/ Shortcuts \/ Default keyboard shortcuts ", 
"snippet" : "When CODESYS Development System is first installed, the following key combinations are set by default. You can customize the default shortcuts to fit your personal requirements. The default keyboard shortcuts are available in the Tools → Customize menu, on the Keyboard tab. You can assign a keyboard...", 
